## Purpose

Quantitative validation that our changes actually improve performance. Benchmarks let us:
1. Prove the improvement (before/after comparison)
2. Prevent regressions (CI checks)
3. Guide optimization (find remaining bottlenecks)

## Key Benchmarks

### 1. Snapshot Swap Latency

The critical metric: how long does it take to swap snapshots in Update()?

```go
// pkg/ui/benchmark_test.go

func BenchmarkSnapshotSwap(b *testing.B) {
    // Create model with existing snapshot
    model := createTestModel(1000) // 1000 issues

