# Critical Path Highlighting

## Context
Highlight the longest dependency chain (critical path) with animated traversal.

## Requirements

### 1. Compute Critical Path via WASM
```javascript
function getCriticalPath() {
    const heights = GRAPH.critical_path_heights();
    const maxHeight = Math.max(...heights);

    // Find the sink with max height
    let sink = null;
    heights.forEach((h, i) => {
        if (h === maxHeight) sink = i;
    });

    // Backtrack to reconstruct path
    return reconstructPath(sink, heights);
}
```

### 2. Visual Highlighting
```javascript
function highlightCriticalPath(path) {
    // Dim all other nodes/edges
    Graph.nodeColor(node => 
        path.includes(NODE_MAP.get(node.id)) 
            ? '#ff6b6b' 
            : '#cccccc50'
    );

    // Thick red edges for critical path
    Graph.linkWidth(link =>
        isOnCriticalPath(link) ? 3 : 0.5
    );
    Graph.linkColor(link =>
        isOnCriticalPath(link) ? '#ff6b6b' : '#cccccc50'
    );
}
```

