# Add Dark Mode Support with System Preference Detection

## Context
Modern web apps should support dark mode. The static viewer should detect system preference and allow manual toggle, persisting the choice.

## Requirements

### Early Theme Detection (No Flash)
In <head> before any content renders:
```html
